 Educational Background



 


Duke University

                  Duke University is an academic university that offers undergraduate, graduate and professional programs. It also has publications and research services. The university was founded in 1838 and is headquartered in Durham, NC.                




 


University of Massachusetts - Amherst

                  UMass Amherst, the flagship campus of the University of Massachusetts system, sits on nearly 1,450-acres in the scenic Pioneer Valley of Western Massachusetts, 90 miles from Boston and 175 miles from New York City. The campus provides a rich cultural environment in a rural setting close to major urban centers.                





 Career History



President

                                    2016 - Current                


Tripwire, Inc.


                  Tripwire, Inc. engages in the provision of risk-based security and compliance management solutions for enterprises, government agencies, and service providers who need to protect sensitive data on critical infrastructure from breaches, vulnerabilities, and threats. It offers a set of foundational security controls including security configuration management, vulnerability management, file integrity monitoring, log, and event management. The firm's products provide organizations control over physical and virtual information technology infrastructure. The company was founded by Wyatt Starnes, Gene Kim, and Eugene H. Spafford in 1997 and is headquartered in Portland, OR.                




Executive Vice President-Industrial Information Technology

                                    2010 - Current                


Belden, Inc.


                  Belden is a worldwide leader in the design, manufacture and marketing of broadcast, enterprise and industrial connectivity and industrial networking and products for many industries including broadcast, oil & gas, data centers, energy, healthcare, and industrial automation.

You can find Belden signal transmission solutions in:

    NFL, MLB and other major sports stadiums
    power, water and water treatment plants
    wind and solar power generation plants
    government and commercial office buildings
    data centers, hospitals and classrooms
    television network and production facilities
    security systems
    high-speed trains and other public transportation


Belden's reliable products and design, engineering and manufacturing excellence enable it to create end-to-end signal transmission solutions that meet the most demanding standards for data, sound, and video applications.

Belden's business is structured in four product platforms: Industrial Connectivity, Industrial Networking, Enterprise Connectivity and Broadcast Solutions.

Belden is headquartered in St. Louis, employs approximately 7,400 people worldwide and has manufacturing capabilities in North America, Europe, and Asia, and a market presence in nearly every region of the world                




Chief Executive Officer

                                    Current                


Prosoft Technology, Inc.


                  Prosoft Technology, Inc. develops communication and connectivity solutions. Its products include remote access, rockwell automation in-chassis, schneider electric in-chassis, gateways, industrial wireless and prosoft software. The firm’s services include knowledge base, regional technical support, legacy downloads, training, return material instructions and literature. The company was founded by Douglas Sharratt in 1988 and is headquartered in Bakersfield, CA.                




President

                                    Prior                


Trapeze Networks, Inc.


                  Trapeze Networks, Inc. provides wireless local area network and mobile applications. The firm's products include RingMaster appliances, SmartPass software, mobility exchanges and system software, and location appliances. The company was founded by William Miskovetz, Dan Simone and Ward Harriman, James Vogt in 2002 and is headquartered in Pleasanton, CA.                





